## Logs Insights

Logs Insights is a CloudWatch feature that analyzes your logs. In Log Insights, you use queries to filter, process, and combine data to help you troubleshoot problems or better understand your network traffic!

I ran the query Top 10 byte transfers by source and destination IP addresses. This query analyzes the top 10 biggest data transfers between IP addresses in my network! I'll find out which resources are moving the most data, which uncovers the busiest traffic routes in my network.

